          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "incident_source": [
                  "D-T"
                ],
                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Neutrons were produced by bombarding Al-backed",
                "Ti-T target with 200 keV deuterons. Neutron energy",
                "was selected by the angular position of the sample.",
                "The neutron energy versus emission angle has been",
                "determined by measuring the activity ratio of Zr-89",
                "and Nb-92m produced in the Zr and Nb foils by (n,2n)",
                "reaction using cross section data from literature.",
                "Neutron energy spreads (1/2FWHM) at En=14.8, 14.4,",
                "14.0 and 13.5 MeV are found to be 210, 130, 40 and",
                "130 keV resp. from literature"
              ]
            }
          ],
